{
  "info": {
    "name": "YARA PICC Notarization",
    "description": "Test collection for YARA LÃ³gica PICC Notarization n8n workflow\n\n## Setup\n\n1. Create an environment with these variables:\n   - `n8n_webhook_url`: Your n8n webhook URL\n   - `hmac_secret`: Your HMAC secret\n\n2. The collection automatically generates HMAC signatures in pre-request scripts\n\n## Test Coverage\n\n- âœ… Valid payloads (minimal, complete, high confidence)\n- âŒ Invalid payloads (bad schema, missing evidence, etc.)\n- ðŸ”„ Idempotency test\n- ðŸ” HMAC authentication test",
